 Command:**\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/router/... -v -run \"TestTokenGeneration\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 5: Implement JWT Token Validation\n**Verifiable Output:** Token validation functionality\n\n- [ ] _TBD: Implement signature verification_\n- [ ] _TBD: Implement expiration checking_\n- [ ] _TBD: Implement claims extraction_\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/router/... -v -run \"TestTokenValidation\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 6: Implement Token Refresh\n**Verifiable Output:** Token refresh mechanism\n\n- [ ] _TBD: Implement refresh token generation_\n- [ ] _TBD: Implement refresh token validation_\n- [ ] _TBD: Implement new token issuance on refresh_\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/router/... -v -run \"TestTokenRefresh\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 7: Create JWT HTTP Handlers\n**Verifiable Output:** HTTP endpoints for JWT operations\n\n- [ ] _TBD: Implement token generation endpoint_\n- [ ] _TBD: Implement public key retrieval endpoint_\n- [ ] _TBD: Add authentication middleware_\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/router/... -v -run \"TestJWTEndpoints\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 8: Add JWT Metrics\n**Verifiable Output:** Prometheus metrics for JWT operations\n\n- [ ] _TBD: Add token generation counter_\n- [ ] _TBD: Add token validation counter_\n- [ ] _TBD: Add validation latency histogram_\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/router/... -v -run \"TestJWTMetrics\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 9: Integration Tests\n**Verifiable Output:** End-to-end integration tests\n\n- [ ] _TBD: Test full token lifecycle_\n- [ ] _TBD: Test K8s Secret integration_\n- [ ] _TBD: Test error scenarios_\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/router/... -v -run \"TestJWTIntegration\" -tags=integration\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task 10: Final Verification\n**Verifiable Output:** All tests pass with coverage\n\n- [ ] _TBD: Run full test suite_\n- [ ] _TBD: Verify coverage >= 80%_\n- [ ] _TBD: Verify no race conditions_\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\ngo test -race ./pkg/router/... -v -coverprofile=coverage.out && \\\ngo tool cover -func=coverage.out | grep jwt.go\n```\n\n---\n\n## Completion Criteria\n\n- [ ] All tasks completed\n- [ ] All unit tests pass\n- [ ] All integration tests pass\n- [ ] Coverage >= 80%\n- [ ] No race conditions detected\n- [ ] Compatible with AR-009\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n- **Total Tasks:** 10\n- **Estimated Total Hours:** _TBD_\n- **Status:** Not Started\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-010/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-011/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-011/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775861740165,"end":1775861740192}}}}
