{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775861740567,"sessionID":"ses_286666ee1ffezKHGLH0SAzeZ19","part":{"id":"prt_d799a47bb0018dE63jLi4kaoBM","messageID":"msg_d799a1b0b001HdWsOUH1kJe62I","sessionID":"ses_286666ee1ffezKHGLH0SAzeZ19","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-011/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-011\ntitle: Router JWT 认证与签发\nmodule: pkg/router\nlanguage: Go\nsize: M\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-011: Router JWT 认证与签发\n# Module: pkg/router\n# Language: Go\n# Size: M\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: jwt-authentication\n  description: |\n    Implement JWT (JSON Web Token) authentication and issuance functionality\n    for the agentcube router. This component handles JWT token generation,\n    signing, validation, and refresh. It provides secure authentication\n    mechanisms for session-based requests, integrating with Kubernetes\n    Secrets for RSA key storage and management.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - JWT token generation and signing\n    - JWT token validation and verification\n    - RSA key pair generation and management\n    - Kubernetes Secret integration for key storage\n    - Token refresh mechanism\n    - JWT claims management (session_id, exp, iat, iss)\n    - Token expiration handling\n    - Public key retrieval endpoint\n  out:\n    - OAuth2/OpenID Connect flows (separate AR)\n    - User identity management (handled by identity provider)\n    - Certificate-based authentication (separate AR)\n    - Token revocation list (separate AR)\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - JWT tokens are signed with RSA-256 algorithm\n  - Tokens include standard claims (exp, iat, iss) and session_id claim\n  - RSA keys are securely stored in Kubernetes Secrets\n  - Token validation succeeds for valid tokens\n  - Token validation fails for expired or invalid tokens\n  - Token refresh mechanism works correctly\n  - Public key can be retrieved for external validation\n  - Unit tests achieve >= 80% coverage\n  - Integration tests verify end-to-end JWT flow\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n  - AR-010: Router 会话管理\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: M\n  story_points: 5\n  days: 4\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-010/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-011/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-011/spec.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-011/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775861740151,"end":1775861740564}}}}
